Further information
Excellent opportunity for an Associate at mid-senior level to join a heavyweight international firm's Corporate department. The team has an excellent track record of working on high quality M&A and joint venture deals in the South East Asian region across a range of sectors such as technology, leisure, retail, and energy. You will be England & Wales qualified and have trained and practiced in a highly rated team (most likely Magic or Silver Circle or elite US firm). Regional experience is strongly preferred though those with experience in another financial centre and a strong motivation to live and work in Singapore will also be considered. Please contact Fred Dos Santos at JLegal in Singapore on +65 6818 9701 or submit your resume to fred@jlegal.com quoting Ref no: FDS - PS 1419 JLegal is acting as an Employment Agency in relation to this vacancy.
